Mandrill,is,an,email,application,and,email,template,service,hosted,by,MailChimp,The,Mandrill,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Mandrill,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,account,and,user,information,retrieving,and,sending,messages,and,sending,templates